title: Pro Discography 2008-2013 (10 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
PRO DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 10 releases...

 * 2008 - Jackin For Hits
 * 2008 - My Name Is  * The Introduction
 * 2009 - Murder Swag - Special Release
 * 2010 - Hold Me Down - Single
 * 2010 - PSA - The Mixtape
 * 2010 - Redemption
 * 2011 - Dying To Live
 * 2011 - PSA Volume 2
 * 2012 - PSA Volume 3 - Who Is Derek Minor
 * 2013 - Minorville

There are those who possess the ability to create greatness from the energy around them. This gift is personified in the music of the artist named Pro. His intense energy and passion for innovation has blasted him into the limelight of unsigned talent from the South.

For Him,
TorrentTracts - December 2013
